                    <div class="service-kicker">SMT stencil</div>
                    <h1>PCB SMT Stencil Support for Reliable Solder Paste Printing</h1>
                    <p class="service-lead">XFPCB provides PCB SMT stencil support for prototype and assembly projects, including aperture, thickness and panel requirements review.</p>
